### Other Components

**USE**: Available components from `@components`

**Available:**
- `Link` - Styled link component
- `CodeBlock` - Code block component
- `Notice` - Notice/alert component
- `ErrorCard` - Error display card
- `Heart` - Heart icon component
- `Icons` - Icon components

**DO NOT**: Recreate these components

```typescript
import { Link, CodeBlock, Notice, ErrorCard } from "@components";

<Link href="https://example.com">External Link</Link>

<CodeBlock language="typescript" code="const x = 1;" />

<Notice type="info">Information notice</Notice>

<ErrorCard>Error message here</ErrorCard>
```

