### Margin Utilities

**USE**: `Margins` from `@components/margins`

**Available classes:**
- `Margins.top8`, `Margins.top16`, `Margins.top20`
- `Margins.bottom8`, `Margins.bottom16`, `Margins.bottom20`
- `Margins.left8`, `Margins.left16`, `Margins.left20`
- `Margins.right8`, `Margins.right16`, `Margins.right20`

**DO NOT**: Create custom margin classes

```typescript
import { Margins } from "@components/margins";

<div className={Margins.top16}>
    Content with top margin
</div>
```

